<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:13:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>耶伦称赞拜登“出色”的经济表现，称美国软着陆已步入正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-lauds-biden-remarkable-economic-performance-says-us-soft-landing-track-2024-07-25/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周四称赞总统乔·拜登“显着的经济复苏”，并表示第二季度GDP和通胀数据证实美国正走上“稳定增长和通胀下降”的道路。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:50:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-lauds-biden-remarkable-economic-performance-says-us-soft-landing-track-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>顶级批评者挑战俄罗斯央行，指责中国降息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/top-critics-challenge-russian-central-bank-point-chinas-rate-cuts-2024-07-25/</link><description>俄罗斯央行准备周五加息，其独立性将受到考验，反对者的压力越来越大，其中包括俄罗斯最具影响力的企业高管伊戈尔·谢钦(Igor Sechin)，后者表示应该向中国学习。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:25:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/top-critics-challenge-russian-central-bank-point-chinas-rate-cuts-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰要求香港不要让俄罗斯规避制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraine-asks-hong-kong-not-let-russia-circumvent-sanctions-2024-07-25/</link><description>乌克兰外交部长德米特罗·库莱巴周四访问香港，并呼吁其领导人李约翰阻止俄罗斯利用香港作为规避西方因莫斯科全面乌克兰战争而对其实施制裁的手段。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 13:23:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraine-asks-hong-kong-not-let-russia-circumvent-sanctions-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>由于制裁阻碍双边贸易结算，俄罗斯和中国转向数字支付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/russia-china-turn-digital-payments-sanctions-hamper-bilateral-trade-settlements-2024-07-25/</link><description>数字平台 Qifa 告诉路透社，俄罗斯和中国之间跨境结算中数字资产的使用增加正在缓解双边支付问题，因为由于制裁，一些直接通过银行进行的结算需要数月时间才能清算。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 13:12:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/russia-china-turn-digital-payments-sanctions-hamper-bilateral-trade-settlements-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>德国默克公司以7.21亿美元向中国GNMI出售颜料业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/germanys-merck-sells-surface-solutions-unit-chinas-gnmi-721-mln-2024-07-25/</link><description>德国多元化集团默克公司周四表示，同意以 6.65 亿欧元（7.2146 亿美元）的价格将其颜料部门出售给中国环球新材料国际公司 (GNMI)。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/germanys-merck-sells-surface-solutions-unit-chinas-gnmi-721-mln-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，巴基斯坦财政部长在北京寻求债务减免</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-finance-minister-beijing-seek-debt-relief-say-sources-2024-07-25/</link><description>两名政府消息人士称，巴基斯坦财政部长穆罕默德·奥朗则布周四抵达北京，就电力部门债务减免以及国际货币基金组织建议的结构改革问题进行会谈。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-finance-minister-beijing-seek-debt-relief-say-sources-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>联合国机构呼吁对亚太地区禽流感病例“令人震惊”的上升采取紧急应对措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/un-fao-urges-urgent-efforts-combat-rise-bird-flu-cases-asia-pacific-2024-07-25/</link><description>联合国粮食及农业组织周四呼吁采取紧急、统一的应对措施，以应对亚太地区人类和动物禽流感病例“令人震惊”的上升。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:01:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/un-fao-urges-urgent-efforts-combat-rise-bird-flu-cases-asia-pacific-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，华为销量激增，苹果中国智能手机出货量下降6.7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-china-smartphone-shipments-leap-while-apple-share-dips-2024-07-25/</link><description>市场研究公司 Canalys 的数据显示，由于苹果面临来自华为 (HWT.UL) 等竞争对手的激烈竞争，2024 年第二季度苹果在中国的智能手机出货量下降了 6.7%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 09:44:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-china-smartphone-shipments-leap-while-apple-share-dips-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官表示，斯特兰蒂斯准备削减品牌并解决美国问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-misses-forecasts-with-h1-drop-revenue-operating-income-2024-07-25/</link><description>Stellantis 首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯 (Carlos Tavares) 周四表示，该公司正在采取措施解决其美国业务利润疲软和库存高企的问题，并将毫不犹豫地削减其庞大投资组合中表现不佳的品牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-misses-forecasts-with-h1-drop-revenue-operating-income-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>市场分析师对中国意外降息的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/market-analysts-react-surprise-rate-cut-china-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国周四非周期削减银行融资成本，令金融市场感到意外。在宣布将一年期中期贷款便利 (MLF) 下调 20 个基点后，股市下跌，债券上涨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:34:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/market-analysts-react-surprise-rate-cut-china-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行再次以较低利率放贷，令人意外</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-surprises-by-lending-again-lower-rates-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国央行周四以极低的利率进行了计划外贷款操作，本周第二次令市场感到意外，这表明当局正试图提供更大规模的货币刺激措施以支撑经济。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:01:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-surprises-by-lending-again-lower-rates-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院驳回大亨黎智英终止审判的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-end-jimmy-lai-trial-2024-07-25/</link><description>香港一家法院周四驳回了法律团队对被监禁的民主人士黎智英结束国家安全审判的请求，称检察官似乎有足够的证据支持对他的所有三项指控。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:52:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-end-jimmy-lai-trial-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求前景黯淡，油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-ease-concerns-over-weak-china-demand-mideast-ceasefire-talks-2024-07-25/</link><description>周四油价下跌，原因是中国消费低迷预示着全球最大原油进口国的需求疲软，超过了周三数据显示美国石油库存大幅减少的支撑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:35:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-ease-concerns-over-weak-china-demand-mideast-ceasefire-talks-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”袭击中国沿海，恐引发大面积洪水</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</link><description>周四，台风“嘉美”横扫台湾海峡，席卷中国东南部，引发了几周前遭受极端降雨袭击的省市河流水位上涨、山洪暴发和内涝的警告。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中资银行下调存款利率以缓解利润率挤压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国五家主要国有银行周四下调了存款利率，以缓解本周意外降低贷款基准以提振经济增长后对本已创纪录低位利润率的打击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>